item.title: By: Michael Huang
item.dc:creator: Michael Huang
item.description:
Hey I'm looking at a used Zeta II that I was considering purchasing. I was wondering if you knew when BRIDE changed fonts from style you have to the current font. I want to put it in either my 89 Civic Si or 93 Starlet GT Turbo and I wanted to be "Era Correct".
Any leads on this info would be appreciated - I've searched without result.
Thanks!
item.content:encoded:
